== About this project

This is an application which reproduce the following bug:
https://rails.lighthouseapp.com/projects/8994/tickets/2451-has_many-through-associations-give-different-results-depending-on-eager-loading-via-include


== How to reproduce the issue

When you execute test i.e. rake test, the test will get failed. See test/unit/user_test.rb


== The way to fix the problem

If you submit the patch named ticket-2451-patch.diff, the issue will be fixed and the test will be passed.

